ADDITIONAL DISCLAIMER

This skill drives your LinkedIn profile through the Claude Chrome extension and
pushes changes to your live account. You are solely responsible for every
change pushed to your profile. The authors are not responsible for account
restrictions, lost content, or any consequence of using this skill. Always
review the backup snapshot the skill creates before approving any change, and
use the official Claude Chrome extension only — never a headless or automated
browser, which may violate LinkedIn's terms of service.
